<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='609000' id='t-609000'>But the pleasant life has three drawbacks,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='613000' id='t-613000'>and it's why positive psychology is not happy-ology and why it doesn't end here.</span>
</span>
