<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='619000' id='t-619000'>The first drawback is that it turns out the pleasant life,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='622000' id='t-622000'>your experience of positive emotion, is heritable,</span>
