<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='663000' id='t-663000'>And, as I said, it's not particularly malleable.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:18
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='667000' id='t-667000'>And this leads to the second life.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='670000' id='t-670000'>And I have to tell you about my friend, Len,</span>
