<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='680000' id='t-680000'>In two of the three great arenas of life, by the time Len was 30,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='684000' id='t-684000'>Len was enormously successful. The first arena was work.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='690000' id='t-690000'>By the time he was 20, he was an options trader.</span>
