<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='718000' id='t-718000'>Len is an introvert.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='722000' id='t-722000'>American women said to Len, when he dated them,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='726000' id='t-726000'>&quot;You're no fun. You don't have positive emotion. Get lost.&quot;</span>
