<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:53
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='762000' id='t-762000'>The question is, is Len unhappy? And I want to say not.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='766000' id='t-766000'>Contrary to what psychology told us about the bottom 50 percent</span>
