<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='795000' id='t-795000'>until 10 days later, the tournament is over, time stops for Len.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:30
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='799000' id='t-799000'>And this is indeed what Mike Csikszentmihalyi has been talking about,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='803000' id='t-803000'>about flow. And it's distinct from pleasure in a very important way.</span>
