</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
14:26
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='855000' id='t-855000'>Just one example. One person I worked with was a bagger at Genuardi's.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='860000' id='t-860000'>Hated the job.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='862000' id='t-862000'>She's working her way through college.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='865000' id='t-865000'>Her highest strength was social intelligence,</span>
