<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='894000' id='t-894000'>So, that's the second path. The first path, positive emotion.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='898000' id='t-898000'>The second path is eudaimonian flow.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
15:13
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='902000' id='t-902000'>And the third path is meaning.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='904000' id='t-904000'>This is the most venerable of the happinesses, traditionally.</span>
