<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
15:38
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='927000' id='t-927000'>I mentioned that for all three kinds of lives, the pleasant life,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='932000' id='t-932000'>the good life, the meaningful life, people are now hard at work on the question,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='937000' id='t-937000'>are there things that lastingly change those lives?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='941000' id='t-941000'>And the answer seems to be yes. And I'll just give you some samples of it.</span>
